channel.description: Fully unique test feed with distinct GUIDs for Zapier detection

item.title: HSBC moves London HQ to 22 Bishopsgate in major workplace overhaul
item.description: HSBC will relocate its global headquarters from Canary Wharf to 22 Bishopsgate, creating a 450,000 sq ft hybrid-ready workspace for 8,000 employees.

item.title: Stormzy to headline New Year’s Eve concert in Trafalgar Square
item.description: The London rapper will perform an exclusive one-night show marking the countdown to 2026.

item.title: Savills signs long-term lease at new City of London offices
item.description: The property consultancy has leased 120,000 sq ft at 100 Leadenhall Street, consolidating multiple teams into one central site.

item.title: Spotify introduces AI-driven playlists for personalised daily mixes
item.description: The feature automatically updates users’ playlists based on real-time listening patterns.

item.title: Lendlease secures planning for 400,000 sq ft office development at Elephant Park
item.description: The developer’s new mixed-use scheme will include offices, retail, and community spaces designed for flexible occupancy.

item.title: Lewis Capaldi announces documentary sequel for Netflix UK
item.description: The follow-up film explores his return to music after a year-long break from touring.

item.title: Cushman & Wakefield opens regional hub in Leeds city centre
item.description: The firm has opened a 90,000 sq ft office on Wellington Street to accommodate teams relocated from Manchester and Sheffield.

item.title: BBC reveals shortlist for next year’s Apprentice candidates
item.description: The business reality show will return in early 2026 with a record number of tech-focused entrepreneurs.

item.title: WeWork launches new flexible workspace at Canary Wharf following restructure
item.description: The operator has opened a 150,000 sq ft co-working campus aimed at financial and fintech tenants seeking short-term leases.

item.title: UK inflation eases to 2.4% as energy prices stabilise
item.description: Economists say the latest figures mark the lowest annual inflation rate since 2021, easing pressure on households.
